      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEAR ME ROAR (8) boasts a strong record this course with 10 wins and 13 minors from 27 tries. In the money last time at this track (17.50) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a half a length second. Looks suited here and rates on top. MISS GLAMOURPUSS (4) has a strong overall record having seven wins and four places from 14 starts including a last start second (22.39) over 400m at Bulli. Meets a moderate line up and should run well. HOTSHOT LILY (7) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.5 lengths (17.47) behind STORMS WILL ROLL at this track. Won at her only start from this draw. Will give a great sight again. TINO BANNER (5) is in the mix after placing here at this trip last time out.",
